<plot>This film is an exploration of art. It attempts to uncover the meaning of art in the dreams of young artists. The artists and their works are set to the music of contemporary Italian musicians, observing the illusion or passion through their eyes and then expressing their work in an original way. In a fantastic setting - seven interviews//art performances created over seven new songs composed for this video by seven of Naples best bands.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?119500</url></doc>
